727207f-a.title: Queens: Lefferts Boulevard - Jamaica Avenue
727207f-a.text:
Lefferts Boulevard, west side, south of Jamaica Ave. (about 190
feet, right not shown). The Queens County Wheelmen's Club was still
in existence in 1912 (people standing in front of club). The house to
the right of the club was No. 277 in 1918.
About 1906.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

727208f-a.text:

the latter being on the extreme right with the subway ''E1'
